-bloodshed-safk-al-dima","tag-call-to-islam-al-dawah","tag-disavowal-bara","tag-unlawful-al-haram","tag-ignorance-jahiliyyah","tag-islam","tag-justice-al-adl","tag-life-al-hiyah","tag-rights-al-huquq","tag-theft-al-sariqah","tag-transgression","tag-treachery-al-ghadr","tag-wealth-al-mal","tag-wrongdoing-al-thulm"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-bC","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":36269,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/21\/islam-plus-hasanat\/","url_meta":{"origin":720,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Tawbah: Embracing Islam plus good deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 21, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Tawil reported: He came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cWhat do you think of a man who commits every sin, leaving nothing of them. Is there repentance for him?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHave you embraced Islam?\u201d He said, \u201cAs for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35269,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/20\/halal-wealth-excellent\/","url_meta":{"origin":720,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Halal: Lawful wealth is excellent for a righteous man","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 20, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Amr ibn al-\u2018As reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, sent for me and he ordered me to put on my armor and weapons, then come to him. I did so and came to him while he was performing ablution. The Prophet raised his eyes to me, then\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_co